name: Mealplanner
0:
”Alexa open my meal plan”
”Alexa launch my meal plan”
”Alexa start my meal plan”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my meal plan
des:
This interactive skill is designed to plan a lunch or dinner. 
Assumption: Skill uses stored personalization and cognition to plan a meal with a user, send recipes, add ingredients to grocery list. 
Future: The goal is to enhance it to communicate emal plan to family, set reminders to buy ingredients or meals, store family preferences, store selections and design questions based on trends like time of day, season, pror selections (cognition).
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
